1.3.0 Release notes (2021-02-08)
=============================================================

### Features

* New config option: 'supportsAppTrackingTransparency' in 'RingPublishingGDPRConfig' class.
* Added support for Apple App Tracking Transparency & onboarding screen before system permission alert is shown.
* New configuration options in 'RingPublishingGDPRUIConfig' related to added ATT onboarding screen:
    - ringPublishingGDPR(_ ringPublishingGDPR: RingPublishingGDPR, didRequestToOpenUrl url: URL)
    - ringPublishingGDPRDidPresentATTOnboardingScreen(_ ringPublishingGDPR: RingPublishingGDPR)
    - ringPublishingGDPR(_ ringPublishingGDPR: RingPublishingGDPR, userSelectedATTOnboardingOptionAllowingTracking allow: Bool)
    - ringPublishingGDPR(_ ringPublishingGDPR: RingPublishingGDPR, userSelectedATTAlertPermisionAllowingTracking allow: Bool)
* New optional delegate methods in 'RingPublishingGDPRDelegate' related to Apple App Tracking Transparency & onboarding screen:
    - brandLogoImage
    - attOnboardingTitle
    - attOnboardingDescription
    - attOnboardingCancelButtonText
    - attOnboardingAllowButtonText

### Changes

* Module initialization parameters: 'gdprApplies', 'tenantId', 'brandName' moved to 'RingPublishingGDPRConfig' class.
* 'RingPublishingGDPR.shouldAskUserForConsents' flag takes into consideration App Tracking Transparency status if it is enabled in configuration.
* 'RingPublishingGDPRUIConfig' class has now mutable fields to allow for easier configuration as it has many more options then before. Only initializer with required properties is provided.
